{"title":"莫斯科（二首）","authors":["尧山壁"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":8,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫斯科（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尧山壁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红场上的３６５天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天都是清明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成千上万的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶来瞻仰列宁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两行长长的队伍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一副吹不去的挽联，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘在风和日丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘在雪天雨中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽联上的文字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由各种发色组成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一个公正的汉字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓墨书写着虔诚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列宁山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在莫斯科常常见到男子一身黑礼服、女子一身白礼服，到列宁山举行结婚典礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵吉祥的长青树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引无数鸟儿来做巢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑、白鸟儿绕树飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啭着甜蜜的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只矫健的苍鹰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"配一只温柔的白鸽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一株青松摇风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴一树梨花带雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烈士纪念碑前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在赫尔岑和他的战友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣誓的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举行海誓山盟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快乐和幸福的起点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此两个生命合而为一："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一首优美的抒情诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"之后是一部长篇小说。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}